Text: Your January OnePass Statement Is Now Onlineyou for choosing to receive Continental Airlines OnePass statement communications electronically Your latest statement is now online providing a summary of your mileage activity through December To access your new statement just visit Your Account at cgibinfloyeCrucuBDUNRG Your mileage activity since your most recent statement is now online hour accessibility paperless archives of your statement and now the most current mileage information your online account tools are better than ever Visit cgibinfloyeCrucuBDURFJM If you have any questions regarding your account please email the OnePass Service Center at mailto and make sure to include your name and OnePass number FE in your email message Sincerely Mark Bergsrud Vice President Marketing UNFORTUNATELY MAIL SENT TO THIS ADDRESS CANNOT BE ANSWERED PLEASE DIRECT ALL INQUIRIES TO mailto OAIRCOM Note To modify your OnePass email preferences please login to Your Account at cgibinfloyeCrucuBDUNRG To unsubscribe from all OnePass email programs please visit cgibinfloyeCrucuBDUvT
